# Trading Checklist Extension Privacy Policy

**Last Updated:** 04.23.2025 

## Data Collection
This Chrome extension ("Trading Checklist") does not collect, store, or transmit any personal or sensitive user data.

## Information Stored Locally
The extension uses Chrome's storage.local API to save only:
- Checklist progress
- Window position preferences
- On/off toggle state

All data remains exclusively on the user's device and is never shared with any servers or third parties.

## Permissions
- `storage`: Required to save checklist state between browser sessions
- `activeTab`: Needed to detect TradingView chart interactions
- `<all_urls>`: Allows the overlay to work across all websites

## Changes to This Policy
Updates will be posted at this URL. Continued use constitutes acceptance.

